videos.description: Trent Forrest takes his defender one-on-one to the rack and banks in a difficult leaning shot to beat the halftime buzzer, giving FSU a 31-30 lead over Miami.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Forrest banks difficult shot to beat halftime buzzer) 2020/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's Forrest banks difficult shot to beat halftime buzzer

videos.description: Harlond Beverly makes up for splitting his free throws by getting the steal on Devin Vassell, then races down the court to stuff down a two-handed dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Miami's Beverly gets the steal and dunks on the break) 2020/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami's Beverly gets the steal and dunks on the break

videos.description: Miami's Chris Lykes turns the ball over, and FSU capitalizes on the fast break as M.J. Walker spots up in the corner to knock down a clutch 3-point shot, tying the game at 69-69.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (FSU's Walker sinks clutch 3-pointer in the corner) 2020/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: FSU's Walker sinks clutch 3-pointer in the corner

videos.description: Florida State's Malik Osborne lets out a roar after he posts his defender and takes him off the dribble to draw the foul and make the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Osborne gets fired up after and-1 bucket) 2020/01/18 ESHEET

videos.headline: Osborne gets fired up after and-1 bucket
